# Project Tech Stack
- Frontend: React (TypeScript)
- Build tool: Vite
- Package manager: Bun
- Styling: CSS (Tailwind etc. can be used as needed)
- AI Tool: Stagewise Toolbar (development only)

# Development Process
- Designed for small teams or solo development (team development is also welcome)
- Code review is optional, but PRs are recommended for important changes
- Communication is primarily in Japanese

# Commit & Push Rules
- Always commit and push when you finish a task or reach a milestone
- Write concise and descriptive commit messages
- Each commit should have a single, clear purpose
- Commit and push frequently

# Other
- Suggestions for improving rules or workflow are welcome
- AI agents must also follow these rules

